</div></div></main><!-- close content main element --></div></div><div id='av_section_1' class='avia-section main_color avia-section-default avia-no-shadow avia-bg-style-scroll  avia-builder-el-8  el_after_av_one_half  el_before_av_section  container_wrap fullsize' style = 'background-color: #ffffff; '  ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-3124'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
<div class="flex_column av_one_half  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding first  avia-builder-el-9  el_before_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-first  " style='border-radius:0px; '><section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color'  style='color:#289bc4; '  itemprop="text" ><h1 style="text-align: left;">What is Author Check?</h1>
</div></section>
<section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><p>AuthorCheck tracks your patrons’ favorite authors and alerts them when a new book arrives at your library. It does this by creating a mirror image of your collection and monitoring any changes. As complicated as that is, it requires no staff time and no software installation. Simply place a small piece of code on your website, and instantly your patrons can access a database of 70,000 popular authors. With a click of their mouse they can add an author to their alert list.</p>
</div></section>
<section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><h3 style="text-align: left;">What makes Author Check so great?</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">Connect patrons directly to their favorite authors through the library and its catalog using Author Check. Through a little widget seamlessly embedded into your libraries website your patrons will be able to setup their own library specific author alerts.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Author Check is completely automated &#8211; no software installation or staff time required. Jut paste a widget on your website to get started today! Your patrons will stay on your website while browsing for their favorite authors and setting up individual alerts for new books arriving at your library. Author Check&#8217;s alert service offers two amazing plugins for your website, allowing your patrons to sign up for author alerts conveniently from your own website. Using state of the art technology our entire author database matches your public library&#8217;s records.</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">Author Check&#8217;s alert service includes a revolutionary author database. Your Author Check account provides you with a link to a magazine styled author database highlighting all of your authors and books as they are added to the public library. Thus, the service never gets boring or outdated. Now that&#8217;s smart!</p>
<p style="text-align: left;">When in-depth biography data, pictures &#038; your library&#8217;s latest acquisitions are meshed together your patrons will discover their library from an entirely new side. Utilize the hidden power of your existing holdings which we convert into an attractive and modern author database that continues to evolve! Across our products we strive to deliver latest web technology to libraries &#8211; to help them save on their budgets and focus on what is really important, while empowering patrons to achieve new insights from existing resources. At the same time our products constantly develop to maximize the use of library information and having fun in the process. We are looking forward to working for you.</p>
</div></section></div><div class="flex_column av_one_half  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-13  el_after_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-last  " style='border-radius:0px; '><div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-   avia-builder-el-14  el_before_av_image  avia-builder-el-first  avia-align-right '  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"  ><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><img class='avia_image ' src='https://www.dearreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Author_Check_sample.png' alt='' title='Author_Check_sample'   itemprop="contentURL"  /></div></div>
<div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-   avia-builder-el-15  el_after_av_image  avia-builder-el-last  avia-align-right '  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"  ><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><img class='avia_image ' src='https://www.dearreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Select_Reads_Sample_3.jpg' alt='' title='Select_Reads_Sample_3'   itemprop="contentURL"  /></div></div></div>

</div></div></div><!-- close content main div --></div></div><div id='av_section_2' class='avia-section main_color avia-section-default avia-no-shadow avia-bg-style-scroll  avia-builder-el-16  el_after_av_section  el_before_av_one_full  container_wrap fullsize' style = 'background-color: #ffffff; '  ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-3124'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
<div class="flex_column av_one_half  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding first  avia-builder-el-17  el_before_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-first  " style='border-radius:0px; '><div class='avia-image-container  av-styling-   avia-builder-el-18  avia-builder-el-no-sibling  avia-align-left '  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject"  ><div class='avia-image-container-inner'><img class='avia_image ' src='https://www.dearreader.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/10/Library_Stock_photo2-495x400.jpg' alt='' title='Library_Stock_photo2'   itemprop="contentURL"  /></div></div></div><div class="flex_column av_one_half  flex_column_div av-zero-column-padding   avia-builder-el-19  el_after_av_one_half  avia-builder-el-last  " style='border-radius:0px; '><section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock  av_inherit_color'  style='color:#289bc4; '  itemprop="text" ><h3 style="text-align: right;">Including a full-fledged author database</h3>
</div></section>
<section class="av_textblock_section"  itemscope="itemscope" itemtype="https://schema.org/CreativeWork" ><div class='avia_textblock '   itemprop="text" ><p style="text-align: right;">Besides widgets to include on your own website allowing patrons to subscribe to their favorite authors, Author check comes with an extensive author database. A smart author database highlighting only authors and books you actually own.</p>
<blockquote><p>“No broken links, no patron frustration. A georgous way of presenting a library&#8217;s holdings by means of presenting authors and their biography data, directly linked into your OPAC.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p style="text-align: right;">Latest arrivals will trigger their authors to be featured on a &#8220;what&#8217;s hot&#8221; list and a magazine-style, state of the art website makes exploring your library even more attractive for your patrons, increasing the usage by presenting your existing information in a new entertaining and user-friendly way.</p>
</div></section></div>
</div></div></div><!-- close content main div --></div></div><div id='after_section_2' class='main_color container_wrap fullsize'   ><div class='container' ><div class='template-page content  av-content-full alpha units'><div class='post-entry post-entry-type-page post-entry-3124'><div class='entry-content-wrapper clearfix'>
